<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>NSHealthShareUsageDescription</key>
    <string>물 섭취 기록과 건강 데이터를 바탕으로 사용자의 수분 섭취를 더 정확하게 안내하기 위해 건강 데이터를 읽습니다.</string>
    <key>NSHealthUpdateUsageDescription</key>
    <string>사용자가 기록한 물 섭취 정보를 건강 앱에 저장해 일관된 건강 기록을 관리할 수 있도록 건강 데이터를 씁니다.</string>
	<key>BASE_URL</key>
	<string>$(BASE_URL)</string>
	<key>CADisableMinimumFrameDurationOnPhone</key>
	<true/>
	<key>CFBundleURLTypes</key>
	<array>
		<dict>
			<key>CFBundleTypeRole</key>
			<string>Editor</string>
			<key>CFBundleURLSchemes</key>
			<array>
				<string>kakao$(KEY_KAKAO)</string>
			</array>
		</dict>
	</array>
	<key>KEY_KAKAO</key>
	<string>$(KEY_KAKAO)</string>
	<key>MARKETING_VERSION</key>
	<string>$(MARKETING_VERSION)</string>
	<key>LSApplicationQueriesSchemes</key>
	<array>
		<string>kakaokompassauth</string>
		<string>kakaolink</string>
		<string>kakaoplus</string>
		<string>kakaotalk</string>
	</array>
	<key>UIBackgroundModes</key>
	<array>
		<string>remote-notification</string>
		<string>healthkit</string>
	</array>
</dict>
</plist>
